data.description: Nestled on private acreage, this charming four-bedroom, three-bathroom brick ranch offers a truly serene retreat. Designed with a spacious layout, a large family room, and a living area that seamlessly blends into the kitchen, creating the perfect space for entertaining guests. The large kitchen offers ample counter space, a walk-in pantry, and a closet pantry. Stepping outside, you'll discover a delightful deck, ideal for hosting gatherings or enjoying peaceful evenings. The patio overlooks the breathtaking natural beauty of the wooded lot, with a tranquil creek meandering through the back of the property. Privacy is paramount, as the home is set back far from the road, ensuring a peaceful and secluded ambiance. Whether seeking a tranquil oasis or a space to create memorable moments with loved ones, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort, beauty, and privacy. Don't miss the opportunity to make this remarkable property your own.
